    "summary": "제19회 자랑스러운 한국 장애인상 정부포상(보건복지부장관 표창) 수상",
    "content": "<h4><strong>2025년 12월 12일 | 보건복지부장관 표창 수상</strong></h4><p>㈜유스트코리아 임순채 대표는 장애인에 대한 인식 개선과 권익 향상을 통해 건강한 사회문화 조성에 기여한 공로를 인정받아, <strong>제19회 자랑스러운 한국 장애인상 시상식</strong>에서<strong>정부포상 부문 보건복지부장관 표창</strong>을 수상하였습니다.</p><figure><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/84d11d13-9c57-4f0c-ab37-3b45041cf22f/06ebb4cd-8b02-4eb8-aa8c-00263f865333/%ED%91%9C%EC%B0%BD%EC%9E%A5%282%29.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466W6HDFYWM%2F20260513%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20260513T142059Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEH4aCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCID4iteVi5kO%2FM9%2B%2BfLR4ypb6ogaE0fIgB6Z65IxH0pk%2BAiBefuXJl4VR5dTC%2BnDD3PWHGjVsmpjx46tPHjokHyNXxCr%2FAwhHEAAaDDYzNzQyMzE4MzgwNSIMr%2B6wkAKz14P7eS8PKtwDuDUEvN%2BG%2BVYWzAFclXSQLg8XTwN%2BGJ3u5t1vdu5OMNHXpuJEURk%2BPLZIQDdeVfTpSa8lpLbhF%2BzNppJ1%2BsgrW6QiBcMqACCxyUjM4F5KgMNZ1wsxEComlkwcMEnjZ735PRNSwZnAqmOcoE6whIly%2B1ZBnAehkOXW79DVGSiAZBlDMRbZbGDvOLmrWc%2ByxT2Wryt484BlrvCa0iwlPe52%2F34ohzkc5NeeyzaCXfRJBqz2ZRu17V0nYCsRry64HDw9xVGPHJgPkEwDBJfzFFQqvYblofCr74VpVh9eR%2F29wXigfbaFveM3tG44J3paX6bDaEARdrymXCdVGolQlhDOi%2F0yY1wTVY%2BbMuVFAtJ3SiZPn2IwifvYAG9PwYP3Qio%2FlyEzunhR9BuG%2FdLat%2Fnt9ZQQ9%2FjDFYErkgbmoMAyyIWekNW3H2%2BMSe1PNTiG%2BFPMCreH%2B%2F0mZ4qEd%2FjGVTVmsjbU9K1qHM7BP1c4nVuysxDoBIfSOmpCcP8qcuGON6hkMgEz0cZjlwT6DxrKvYAYut8RqTX8dXdquF0jzJBnFx1SEmNeBHFZuXleR1ZVJct3IS2fBjAlIXj3r1XQ3bmGAMjEnqC%2BySg1GtLtaYxMv8A4Wvy5lzPk8Td%2Fo7Mwi%2FqR0AY6pgH7lorU2V6Mk%2BTZWuKjjayDTYXrAWsHC4yU5CYbaETVTmOqdzegMaj6i7eCJ3Uul1t2pjk3DDDme2iAyzZmubFMZkI562qSq8tttJ67RTCxHXrwgTod3Avu9s9mv3JcqCMMeQKdtJIBoOfv1C%2BFDxuxcsHwxdYlqJkondDuSZEDMUZEt7pXDXHP7NLS5zaAgi2EqG2IO8XmD4oCEr16%2BIETjoIkU%2FA5&X-Amz-Signature=ce43088850aa3d7a0b429f53aa15c01a1503a84cca93141470fcd253d7a9aec9&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&x-id=GetObject\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-