    "category": "행사/활동",
    "summary": "스위스 본사와 고객이 소통, 브랜드 철학·웰빙 가치 공유 및 제품 체험",
    "content": "<h4><strong>2025년 4월 25일 | Swiss JUST Beauty Class 개최</strong></h4><p>Swiss JUST Beauty Class를 통해</p><p>스위스 본사와 고객이 직접 소통할 수 있는 자리를 마련하였습니다.</p><p>본 클래스에서는 스위스의 문화와 유스트 본사의 역사 그리고 브랜드가 추구해 온 철학과 웰빙 가치가 공유되었으며,</p><p>고객이 유스트 제품을 직접 경험할 수 있는 시간으로 운영되었습니다.</p><figure><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/84d11d13-9c57-4f0c-ab37-3b45041cf22f/94efec27-22bc-4a65-b7e0-112d326d51ba/IMG_8040.jpeg?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466XOHB2Y3L%2F20260513%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20260513T142100Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEH4aCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIHKLULH62mHrriwbrFdixpVUoJRJAkgd0PLstvYk7ONmAiEA7mYqwZT8Gc2ZFU%2BpJpTWmJfBuFQx7BM%2BxXIwmtEAEyAq%2FwMIRxAAGgw2Mzc0MjMxODM4MDUiDEhz2LgiiJF6eeqvSircA4IhhCYVoJ2zvIn%2BfP%2F8oZF7J1nCyFiTz40L%2BaxotmDoTrtlCvkb3nAZVwj12kW%2BSvIv0BmSoUTkUbPP4WF4lrHuvKEnXE5G57ogSKSKfgQWkEu4pJ9xznK%2B9uSFn8QOmNZvdunrob7yak5fXbtgfAKdaXTYyHMlI7RVcjyEgf%2BlYc39sNllQuuZwQEN3F75DVgaDcKWZLDFsP4rYl7YkKW7uQgjTdjt6P3NTaTUa8KO4yuAO19c%2BdDXYNXj6QnUxb3L56aJM%2BLZirk8ipuaA56MakyLI2uK0JzBgiIbo%2FPAKqP8M%2FptWZOr3TFrnIWJay2Hm89z0%2FBgHLVU8KjTbZTMz3A0jxbDWJvRJF1Ok4la84WGTt9VLIf1zXFsTh5Gz%2Bwgf5GYkQ5Wve%2BCcyxWXo3QxzhbsE%2F8rS0c8qiStmhdEPJI5oWcXVmjOE0utDOakH4yB39NINrlAIOb7LQxr2wmZPy%2FRSwX%2FZw6DLRDdG37288Ync%2B9hCKo8xBoTUUX1hOxbvPYClexIadD2oRZncNqrUrTNX83Budffi5sIPDaSuP6PbaOdAv9kLIRBWD0I0dsCMkL3qvV01nJo2Cx2e3Nh9MlWq0duuklwBluIDiafortmEJsxO9OdOBqMK75kdAGOqUBzSHyJRAanZliJ2NcFjwlQBcQ7MPX7f%2BTl%2Btw5noK0dxHAs0Wc%2BNAWQiGC4rTwoBq5MZjhHDFzrOGWBd1ISbaqftZgXd%2FnipgvC1RgpQuvwzUw7zoE2dQ2jrYp0sejTAVac%2B74gIYa7w346Iu8gR5JpCKKrUSVNXhJNHQ0R9WLMsp6bB1kaXwy5GCopw4XXmcpQvnUgCXkrr%2FErU6HLb96Gp4oY60&X-Amz-Signature=ceb5b9d47af9523f99797b5fcc43d3c32f8851c8321af0ec0e1fe7298ee94b1d&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&x-id=GetObject\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.