    "content": "<h4><strong>2025년 4월 23일 | 스위스 본사–한국 본사 공동 미팅</strong></h4><p>㈜유스트코리아는</p><p>스위스 본사 임직원과 한국 본사 임직원 및 전국 매장 직원이 함께하는</p><p>공동 미팅을 한국에서 진행하였습니다.</p><p>유스트는 본사와의 긴밀한 협업을 통해 글로벌 기준에 부합하는 품질과 신뢰를 유지하며,</p><p>한국 고객에게 적합한 웰빙 경험을 제공하기 위해 지속적으로 노력하고 있습니다.</p><figure><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/84d11d13-9c57-4f0c-ab37-3b45041cf22f/aa8ffbe4-8c20-4e50-ae9c-944be6972b81/IMG_7998.jpeg?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466XLHKKKSN%2F20260513%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20260513T142102Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEH4aCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIF7IbV0tno1KdhRRq8rzct4e%2BdOh%2F%2B9El6O8wLt07ieZAiEAvAKE8DYVgTChYmfh1BiufR%2Bnz%2FVdC31rz6lyVOVJkxwq%2FwMIRhAAGgw2Mzc0MjMxODM4MDUiDAYnKMGUqnWasSZESyrcA4LSTe2cIeWIDYMfAFKxPIk%2Fb1gNAWWazOZu8Jfo6sw230%2BuBtjCWbn%2BmsWPA78ccssMFExcbaddMbARdGZgFGNDXDjBXT7GVrY9GNcpDUxQ83ZVP9A0yf07yNMhCCxmBAPDCt7YQVX%2FJFL7Dw2uwnkizr%2B%2Fe6UUdhk0AUFqDWSsn%2FBj9KiYU%2FS0eJEXWdwRqEd8zXCQ6UpuselLMr1itEwkpgJYMrfI%2BczIAOORcOhnCZBow%2FFan0qkyfTrlmdzyAFgg5lINWNKp5Eu8Qygjt2BLkDUiDJzw75IASs2bGYDMRGkEydJ7DcvGVoCEgDseOJxUer%2BjGCmUayze06p4ZKxVJtUnW3S7HE7FIVdIPDSqkffOFnmSuvtFPmartzYXqAg%2F%2F5nLMEl7U7UvjMqtx2qgNdStOQ0FXIaBRXD863BXjE4ItS6lGDqXor%2FKdJ4Gh7mYJ%2B4qXTamw0vB2KV07NKhVqNgrB%2F3qZUPdV9v0eYLI88LO1h7pfmmlay7N0Qj5rKy6QIvG49jPX6bIPdn6i7hjqj47h3tKBZ0kEFHOO1Iws26ux9Gnh12jGDay5wv3BvRCuQWh1wAp%2FRwjg4cxQedoEv8Li%2FCwDrm%2Fv44QvxAqnxfJeB8Vm8hRdsMPb3kdAGOqUBwZFHW6%2FNQGBDCl2LaXbgNNxIbnPwZ5nsIE%2BekoMCRhmeDuutiL7JzAw%2B1in8UpuVMtB7zc9zL7Zu0ksNIGS57FQe3T6ySlHVZzZQMPfNTkSRpfCccayqQgoHdY2DSaJShyVc9E05WSfx6%2F%2FMP3yo2WnhUPgO4VA5hSJfMUGYQpklRjleYQSpgraoP2CmZksrlwt6w2YlXpkzOG404cfRO%2FGYrlSv&X-Amz-Signature=6beaf62e84446a2b4f57e38e4ec58e19f3cc0bed5c89298f7bb5247762390a96&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&x-id=GetObject\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure>"
