    "summary": "산불 피해 대피소 방문, 아로마 테라피 마사지 회복 지원",
    "content": "<h4><strong>2025년 4월 | 의성–안동 산불 피해 지원 활동</strong></h4><p>의성–안동 산불은 대한민국 역사상 가장 큰 규모와 인명 피해를 기록한 대형 산불이었습니다.</p><p>유스트는 안동시 다목적 체육관에 마련된 대피소에 직접 방문하여,</p><p>아로마 테라피 마사지를 통해 피해 주민들의 심신 안정과 신체적 불편 완화를 돕는 회복 지원 활동을 진행하였습니다.</p><figure><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/84d11d13-9c57-4f0c-ab37-3b45041cf22f/3a9fe533-6965-4464-9dd8-fd60fc8b1484/IMG_7410.jpeg?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB4662EV4HQ7M%2F20260513%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20260513T142102Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEH4aCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIB4yR3nBglvnSpzaV8vg2kWg2mXEr5tawOnpnEnzKq%2BAAiEA8eKVavc0ieDezhOePTWLHVpO0NZ7GzSObvZ7ub7OeAcq%2FwMIRxAAGgw2Mzc0MjMxODM4MDUiDAM1ZK0OJTfs2Y5EOCrcA2HscxMlMjPvuIIarurAW%2BLsq3%2BQJowrQpdCfm6nmoS8VnlwkYsCFCarCDRdiE7IVPBOhjUgV%2Fb1RJCcluBOwq61VQIwoCT3J1t1NuS0DqCOakQFyn3oF9DEk9MXP%2Fv3NVUevwYwkv77EFFk9Y8DkAYnLb91wJmX07ILfuAWPQEf7ICxMTaD3ElMHQR3CtH%2Br8%2ByxkNX2dX5WlpAURAfSdpffli6U9pwhGNlfR7MuJLxImDKChBgfzY4voJmDV0whdNh1JNS5R2CqYIDP5zUny%2BPQXqrPJLNgbF9zXrNRqZv77yXTBW%2FQfcAXBaUeGcpuD%2B9aovBWvVJy%2BuOnqOgmEkXdSSlt4CwsuGMfpPy3nso2as1GG9Mk9Or7WEpyMDYpLQlB9LJHW4YrbxtaIxlcor05tulenFL83Rrva%2FvuO3rnNILWoHMdvY4k%2FFnBNR9fCGgj3MqpCZojS96T1Wv1onORHb541yiUyBkdiDT%2BS98jtsjIAIcwV1sVbRUAf3BCfxb5mrd3ejmF01gK1n2VX8JbJvkUbWUZOOz8pirRMjPYeMn0tFmfkaCVsRcsTHSiaRLQXvlT5cnJg8AwPVRFCkFt96MwhvF%2BH00DF8eKoa5x88E2A84uIX4Gy3QMJP5kdAGOqUBAjLwynKIQvMwMCTzI5QI75HjXDhk1s9ANDo2L9ugHL6VgRG%2F2hxz7XqBSAOUneRdnEjWpCbSzE9qzA0ip7A6toGsv201CXRdfcj1Z8bxoypOXDCbXHWWMwlO6XxgPqq1qOnrOdgFh%2FaXc4p%2FD2dArh0ufF%2BaBSKP2w0qQ97chqD4sQyvSRl5szjVwdQPMFquDoGuttZ0jge8Z4sy9cSIehKA61jT&X-Amz-Signature=1be5e95f4142df7a7c44997f1c4df25aede7cdee4683417e1ece6a0a7911dd00&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&x-id=GetObject\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/84d11d13-9c57-4f0c-ab37-3b45041c